<body onload="Gamestart()">
<div class="container-fluid">
    <h4 class="green-text center" align="center"><i>Tic-Tac-Toe Game for Double Player</i> </h4>
    <br>
    <div class="row">
        <div class=" col-lg-8 col-md-6 " align="center">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-md-push-3">
            <table class="table-bordered centered" >
            <tr>
                <td id="1" class="square" onclick="move(this);">
                <td id="2" class="square" onclick="move(this);">
                <td id="3" class="square" onclick="move(this);">
            </tr>

            <tr>
                <td id="4" class="square" onclick="move(this);">
                <td id="5" class="square" onclick="move(this);">
                <td id="6" class="square" onclick="move(this);">
            </tr>

            <tr>
                <td id="7" class="square" onclick="move(this);">
                <td id="8" class="square" onclick="move(this);">
                <td id="9" class="square" onclick="move(this);">
            </tr>
            <input type="button" class="waves-effect waves-light btn btn-round blue" value="New Game" onclick="reset();" name="newGame"/>

            <br><br><br>
            </table>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="panel panel-info blue-grey-text">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h1 class="panel-title"><b><h4 align="center">Tic-Tac-Toe Game </h4></b></h1>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <h5 class="center"><b>RULES</b></h5>

                    <ol type="1">
                        <li> The Game is Played on 3*3 matrix (i.e 3 Squares by 3 Squares )</li><br>
                        <li> Player 1 is X , and Player 2 is O .</li><br>
                        <li> Player take turns putting their marks in empty squares.</li><br>
                        <li> The first player to get 3 of his marks in top , down , across or diagonal is the
                            winner .
                        </li><br>
                        <li> When all the 9 square are full , the game is over. If no player has 3 marks in a row then
                            the game is tie .
                        </li><br>
                    </ol>
                    <h5 class="center"><b>Enjoy the Game</b></h5>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<br>
